<collectingCountry id="F31312BEFF9CFFB2CDC6FC69FABFB7A0" box="[1166,1281,938,964]" name="Argentina" pageId="9" pageNumber="202">Argentina</collectingCountry>
. In the State of São Paulo, the species is known by only 
<specimenCount id="9D0299A7FF9CFFB2CB19FC0EFD53B783" box="[593,749,973,999]" pageId="9" pageNumber="202" type="generic">one specimen</specimenCount>
, collected between rocks in a pasture.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BBB522EFF9CFFB2C9F5FC2CFA23B06D" blockId="9.[136,1452,938,1312]" box="[189,1437,1007,1034]" pageId="9" pageNumber="202">
